{{DISPLAYTITLE:min and max}}
These simple but useful functions return the least or greatest of two parameters.
<pre>
function int min (int a, int b)
{
	if (a < b)
		return a;

	return b;
}

function int max (int a, int b)
{
	if (a > b)
		return a;

	return b;
}
</pre>

[[category:Sample ACS functions]]
